OL,4,CMitsubishi Colt bought 25 years ago
OL,5,Crecalled over airbag fault
OL,6, A man said it was "bizarre" his car had
OL,7, been recalled over an airbag defect 25
OL,8, years after he bought it.
OL,10,FStuart Rippin from Wickford, Essex,
OL,11,Fsaid he received a letter saying his
OL,12,F1996 Mitsubishi Colt had an outstanding
OL,13,Fvehicle safety recall.
OL,15,FThe fault with Takata airbags was first
OL,16,Fidentified in 2007, with about 100
OL,17,Fmillion vehicles recalled globally.
OL,19,FMr Rippin said the car, which he bought
OL,20,Fnew, had "given me no trouble for all
OL,21,Fthe 25 years".
